{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"tool_use_id": "chatcmpl-tool-8c9b32945d74afa0", "type": "tool_result", "content": "# \narXiv: 2605.00329\nAuthors: \nYear: 0 | Venue: \nTopic: tts_vc\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. The energy-distance objective is applied to text-to-audio generation for the first time, enabling low-latency one-step latent synthesis.\n  2. An auxiliary distillation loss aligns feature representations from a diffusion-based teacher transformer with the energy-based student model, yielding consistent improvements across all objective metrics.\n  3. The proposed model outperforms existing few-step sampling baselines on both objective and subjective metrics while narrowing the quality gap to multi-step diffusion systems.\n\nTags: TTS, TTS/架构-NAR-Diffusion, TTS/功能-蒸馏加速, TTS/功能-快速生成", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "6fa048a7-4bf3-481f-994f-575f3d4d1d44", "uuid": "dbd36019-c44f-4067-b3e8-ee98ee42c40d", "timestamp": "2026-07-14T17:39:17.771Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "# \narXiv: 2605.00329\nAuthors: \nYear: 0 | Venue: \nTopic: tts_vc\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. The energy-distance objective is applied to text-to-audio generation for the first time, enabling low-latency one-step latent synthesis.\n  2. An auxiliary distillation loss aligns feature representations from a diffusion-based teacher transformer with the energy-based student model, yielding consistent improvements across all objective metrics.\n  3. The proposed model outperforms existing few-step sampling baselines on both objective and subjective metrics while narrowing the quality gap to multi-step diffusion systems.\n\nTags: TTS, TTS/架构-NAR-Diffusion, TTS/功能-蒸馏加速, TTS/功能-快速生成", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
